460
00:46:30,005 --> 00:46:34,217
Kita akan berjumpa lagi. Kau
tahu kami akan di sini. Semoga.

461
00:46:34,301 --> 00:46:38,138
Besok malam ada Diana
Hudson, Greg Gordon...

462
00:46:38,221 --> 00:46:41,558
dan pakar hewan, Hugh Little.

463
00:46:41,642 --> 00:46:45,604
