00:47:04,206 --> 00:47:05,832
Oh, Happy.

468
00:47:08,418 --> 00:47:10,253
Happy, aku menulis surat baru.

469
00:47:10,337 --> 00:47:12,172
Ayo, berdansalah denganku.

